    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nmany ghost windows are listed when vim._extui is enabled\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n1. minimal.lua:\n\n```lua\nrequire(\"vim._extui\").enable({})\nvim.print(vim.api.nvim_list_wins())\n```\n\n2. run `nvim --clean -u minimal.lua`\n\nprint:\n\n```\n{ 1000, 1005, 1004, 1003, 1001 }\n```\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nprint:\n\n```\n{ 1000 }\n```\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\nNVIM v0.12.0-dev-490+gee84518b94\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nno\n\n### Operating system/version\n\n6.14.7-arch2-1\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nst 0.8.5\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nst-256color\n\n### Installation\n\nAUR",
